# Test: Form Fill and Submit
# URL: https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/forgot_password
# Tags: forms, regression

Navigate to https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/forgot_password
Verify that the page contains "Forgot Password"
Click the Email field
Type "test@example.com" in the email address input field
Take a screenshot named "form-filled"
Click the Retrieve Password button
Wait for 2 seconds
Verify that the page contains "Your e-mail's been sent"
Take a screenshot named "form-submitted"
